{"tid":481150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵酒醉女同事　他「包皮過長」留鐵證","createTime":"2017-11-27T01:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T03:42:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec5ebb25b8be25dff54a9f246619edc946f3e9b","tid":481150,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"南投林姓男子心儀同公司女同事，兩人在2015年2月間前往主管喜宴，女同事不勝酒力，林將女同事載往摩鐵，趁機性侵得逞。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，林替女同事解開襯衫扣子，女同事在浴室內，脫掉內衣褲後，倒在浴缸，林見狀趁機性侵。她事後發現內褲有血，起疑提告。判決書指出，林男患有包皮過長、乾閉性陰莖頭炎等疾病，性侵女同事過程中出血留下證據。林坦承犯案，但認為判刑過重，上訴二審。二審審理時，雙方達成和解，合議庭撤銷原判決，依乘機性交罪，判刑1年8月，緩刑2年，緩刑期間責付保護管束。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.amazonaws.com/br-cdn/temp_images/2013/10/06/williamn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fbr-cdn%2Ftemp_images%2F2013%2F10%2F06%2Fwilliamn.gif&h=20445749&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13f49f47edfcd1216d6658cb06f6ecdcce1d63d3","tid":481150,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402462929638882af904e3a7ec0dfbba1a4d3cc3","tid":481150,"uid":1911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"性侵女同事過程中出血留下證據。"},{"pid":"d07b2cc1f642cc8944340bf2f023243571e0f166","tid":481150,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:34:24.000Z","msg":"on9仔"},{"pid":"04ea2839322e0b90f165ae70654ab071204dba74","tid":481150,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"緩刑兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004a059c4e6ed8ac8c3421dcae1ab1173943dce1","tid":481150,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"強姦人都唔駛坐"},{"pid":"612b93d024192ac14ac2098441c9999faea8a9ca","tid":481150,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep